snippet.title: Cosmo Vulpes - Alpha Version | SAGE 2022
snippet.description:
Cosmo Vulpes is an in development 3D platformer where your main tool is the jetpack. Play as Klaus, a bounty hunter fox, and with his jetpack and other gadgets made by his friend fennec Safira, complete his missions and explore new worlds!
• Use the jetpack to traverse large distances and explore the environments!
• High-Tech Gadgets allows to have even more mobility and combat options!
• Face Amber, the first rivals, try to complete her challenge!

This trailer contains footage from an Alpha Version. Game content may change.
